Customer Relations Management Software Options:

Far too many CRM free editions are trials and/or limited to less than 3 users, and we have at least 4 employees listed in our email exchange with Mr. Roberts.

If they have a budget (which I doubt since this is a class, and not real), then the options open up.

One or two good open source options were ruled out for having heavy-setup and maintenance needs and/or presumed a server and upkeep administration.

Viable options:
https://www.hubspot.com - so far this is the only one I have been able to actually experience

